### Quick Test for Login Functionality
### Use this file to quickly test the basic login functionality

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Quick Registration and Login Test

### 1. Register a test user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "QuickTest Company",
  "companyEmail": "quick@test.com",
  "companyPhone": "0123456789",
  "companyAddress": "Test Address",
  "taxCode": "123456789",
  "username": "quickuser",
  "email": "quickuser@test.com",
  "fullName": "Quick User",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "password": "QuickTest123!",
  "role": "admin"
}

### 2. Login with the registered user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "quickuser",
  "password": "QuickTest123!"
}

### 3. Test invalid login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "quickuser",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}